By adding an onFocus in the Textarea that explicitly sets the cursor position to the end of the text. 
i think this is the root issue, so no need of any useEffect or anything.
```
onFocus={(e) => {
  const length = e.currentTarget.value.length;
  e.currentTarget.setSelectionRange(length, length);
}}
```

